{"id":18801,"date":"2025-05-29T10:55:53","date_gmt":"2025-05-29T10:55:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/?p=18801"},"modified":"2025-05-29T11:10:29","modified_gmt":"2025-05-29T11:10:29","slug":"6valley-v15-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/6valley-v15-2\/","title":{"rendered":"6Valley V15.2: Setup Guideline, Dynamic Backgrounds &amp; Logo"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>We\u2019re excited to announce the release of <strong>6Valley version 15.2<\/strong>! This update brings powerful new features and thoughtful redesigns aimed at making your experience smoother and\u00a0better than ever.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Here\u2019s an overview of the latest features:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The setup guidelines feature in the Admin Panel<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dynamic background color customize&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Invoice logo add, remove, and customize<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Business pages, which will be shown on the footer&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Currency update flow for better accuracy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>SMS testing with Firebase and third-party gateways<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>File Manager with search and recent files<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Module-based permissions for employee roles<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Others Improvements<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Guidelines Feature In Admin Panel&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A setup guide pop-up is always displayed in the admin panel. It lists the essential steps to complete before starting your business. Sometimes, admins are unsure about which settings they need to configure before starting their business. This setup guide helps them by clearly showing what needs to be done.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"452\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/6valley-admin-panel.webp\" alt=\"6Valley Admin Panel\" class=\"wp-image-18810\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/6valley-admin-panel.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/6valley-admin-panel-300x151.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/6valley-admin-panel-768x386.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path : 6Valley Admin Panel<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Suppose the admin needs to complete 10 steps in the setup guide. When the admin clicks the pop-up, a list of all the steps is shown. Completed steps have a blue checkmark next to them. Steps that are not yet completed still need to be finished. A percentage is also displayed to show how much of the setup is complete.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"838\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-guide-popup.webp\" alt=\"Setup Guide Popup\" class=\"wp-image-18812\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-guide-popup.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-guide-popup-300x279.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-guide-popup-768x715.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: 6Valley Admin Panel> Setup Guide Popup<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, the admin is required to set the general setup. The admin should select the general setup option to configure the general settings. This will take them directly to the general setup page and show a side popup with a brief description explaining why it is important.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"464\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-setup-page-1.webp\" alt=\"General Setup Page\" class=\"wp-image-18813\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-setup-page-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-setup-page-1-300x155.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-setup-page-1-768x396.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Setup Guide Popup> General Setup Page<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><br>After completing all the necessary steps in the general setup, the admin will have the option to save the information. If any mistakes are made, there is also an option to reset the setup.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"565\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-save-information.webp\" alt=\"General Setup Page&gt;\" class=\"wp-image-18815\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-save-information.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-save-information-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/general-save-information-768x482.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Setup Guide Popup> General Setup Page> Save Information\u00a0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once the information is updated, the number of remaining steps in the setup guide will automatically decrease. The completed setup will immediately show a blue checkmark, indicating that it is finished.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"788\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-complete-preview.webp\" alt=\"Setup Complete Preview\u00a0\" class=\"wp-image-18816\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-complete-preview.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-complete-preview-300x263.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/setup-complete-preview-768x672.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Setup Guide Popup> Setup Complete Preview\u00a0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This example shows a basic setup to help you understand the process. The admin can use it to complete all the required setup.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dynamic Color Customization&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The admin can customize the admin panel colors in the admin panel website setup, which is located under the business setup. In that section, they will find color settings where they can make the changes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"318\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/website-setup.webp\" alt=\"Website Setup\" class=\"wp-image-18817\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/website-setup.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/website-setup-300x106.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/website-setup-768x271.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Business Setup> Website Setu<\/em>p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Panel sidebar color is used only for the background of the panel sidebar menu. The primary light color is used for website cards and sections. But for the panel sidebar, it is recommended to use a dark color to make the text easier to see.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"476\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/color-settings.webp\" alt=\"Color Settings\" class=\"wp-image-18818\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/color-settings.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/color-settings-300x159.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/color-settings-768x406.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Business Setup> Website Setup> Color Settings<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Invoice Logo Add, Remove, and Customize<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If the admin wants to customize, add, or remove the invoice logo, they can do it from the business setup section. There, they will find a section called &#8220;Invoice.&#8221;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"336\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/invoice.webp\" alt=\"Invoice\" class=\"wp-image-18819\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/invoice.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/invoice-300x112.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/invoice-768x287.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Business Setup> Invoice<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the invoice settings, there is an option called &#8220;Logo of the Invoice,&#8221; where the admin can update the logo or keep the current one. If the admin wants to remove the logo from the invoice, they just need to turn off the toggle button.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/logo-on-invoice.webp\" alt=\"Logo On Invoice\u00a0\" class=\"wp-image-18820\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/logo-on-invoice.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/logo-on-invoice-300x167.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/logo-on-invoice-768x427.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Business Setup> Invoice> Logo On Invoice\u00a0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Business Pages Feature&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The admin can add new business pages from the Business Pages List section under Pages &amp; Media. A maximum of 10 new pages can be added to the list. The added pages will be shown in the website footer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/business-pages.webp\" alt=\"Business Pages\" class=\"wp-image-18821\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/business-pages.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/business-pages-300x156.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/business-pages-768x399.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Pages &amp; Media> Business Pages<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To add a new page, the admin needs to click on &#8220;Add New Pages.&#8221; Then, they just need to add an image, title, and page description to create the page. There is also a toggle option to turn the page on or off. If the admin wants to temporarily disable a page, they can use this option.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"523\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/add-new-business-pages.webp\" alt=\"Add new business Page\" class=\"wp-image-18823\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/add-new-business-pages.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/add-new-business-pages-300x174.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/add-new-business-pages-768x446.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> Business Settings> Pages &amp; Media> Business Pages> Add New Business Pages> Save Information<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Currency Update&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From the System Setup, the admin can add any new currency they want to include. This helps in managing different types of currencies from various countries.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"569\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/system-setup.webp\" alt=\"Currency Update\u00a0\" class=\"wp-image-18824\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/system-setup.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/system-setup-300x190.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/system-setup-768x486.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> System Settings> System Setup> Currency > Add New Currency > Submit<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If the admin wants to keep only one default currency, they can do that by setting its status to &#8220;Default.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"459\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/currency-list.webp\" alt=\"Currency List\" class=\"wp-image-18825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/currency-list.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/currency-list-300x153.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/currency-list-768x392.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> System Settings> System Setup> Currency >Currency List> Set Status<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">SMS Configuration Testing<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For the SMS configuration module, the admin can choose which system will send verification or notification messages to users via SMS.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If the admin connects an external SMS service provider, such as Twilio, Nexmo, or Msg91, the messages will be sent through that third-party provider.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, if the admin enables Firebase OTP, the messages will be handled by Firebase.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"474\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/3rd-party-setup-sms-configuration.webp\" alt=\"SMS Configuration Testing\" class=\"wp-image-18827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/3rd-party-setup-sms-configuration.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/3rd-party-setup-sms-configuration-300x158.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/3rd-party-setup-sms-configuration-768x404.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> 3rd Party Setup > Other Configuration > SMS Configuration<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">File Manager with Search and Recent Files Functionality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Earlier, the file manager did not have options to select, search, or copy files. But now, in the admin panel, the file manager includes options to select files, copy images, and search files by name.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"468\" src=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/file-manager.webp\" alt=\"File Manager with Search and Recent Files Functionality\" class=\"wp-image-18826\" srcset=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/file-manager.webp 900w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/file-manager-300x156.webp 300w, https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/file-manager-768x399.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Path: Admin Panel> System Settings> Gallery > File Manager\u00a0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kb-btns18801_0aa9ad-34{gap:var(--global-kb-gap-xs, 0.5rem );justify-content:center;align-items:center;}.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-button{font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;}.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0{margin-right:5px;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button{color:#555555;border-color:#555555;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{color:#ffffff;border-color:#444444;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button::before{display:none;}.wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:hover, .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn.kt-btns18801_0aa9ad-34 .kt-btn-wrap-0 .kt-button:focus{background:#444444;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn kb-buttons-wrap kb-btns18801_0aa9ad-34\"><style>ul.menu .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kb-btn18801_c366fb-67.kb-button{width:initial;}<\/style><a class=\"kb-button kt-button button kb-btn18801_c366fb-67 kt-btn-size-standard kt-btn-width-type-auto kb-btn-global-fill kt-btn-has-text-true kt-btn-has-svg-false  wp-block-kadence-singlebtn\" href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/ecommerce-cms-solution-demo\/\"><span class=\"kt-btn-inner-text\"><strong>Click Here to Explore the Demo<\/strong><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other Improvements &amp; Modifications<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides that, 6Valley has special design and feature improvements to make it look better and work more smoothly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Redesigned several User app screens (Categories, Track Order, Product Details, etc.)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Module-based permissions for employee roles<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improved business setup UI\/UX in the Admin Panel<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improved chat experience<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Optimized assets for faster and smoother app performance<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>That\u2019s all for this update. Team 6Valley is working on more amazing features, so keep watching for what\u2019s next in 6Valley!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We\u2019re excited to announce the release of 6Valley version 15.2! This update brings powerful new features and thoughtful redesigns aimed at making your experience smoother and\u00a0better than ever. Here\u2019s an overview of the latest features: Guidelines Feature In Admin Panel&nbsp; A setup guide pop-up is always displayed in the admin panel. It lists the essential &#8230; <a title=\"6Valley V15.2: Setup Guideline, Dynamic Backgrounds &amp; Logo\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/6valley.app\/blog\/6valley-v15-2\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about 6Valley V15.2: Setup Guideline, Dynamic Backgrounds &amp; Logo\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":18807,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[211],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-18801","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-update"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18801","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18801"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18801\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/18807"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18801"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18801"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18801"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}